{"word":"G2065 - ἐρωτάω - erōtáō - er-o-tah'-o - Ask","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐρωτάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">erōtáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">er-o-tah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Ask</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேண்டு, கேள், விசாரி, வினாவு"},{"paragraph":"1. to question"},{"paragraph":"2. to ask, to request, entreat, beg, beseech,"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Apparently from <a href=\"#/G2046 - ἐρέω - eréō - er-eh'-o/2046\">G2046</a> (compare <a href=\"#/G2045 - ἐρευνάω - ereunáō - er-yoo-nah'-o/2045\">G2045</a>); to <i>interrogate</i>; by implication to <i>request</i>: - ask, beseech, desire, intreat, pray. Compare <a href=\"#/G4441 - πυνθάνομαι - pynthánomai - poon-than'-om-ahee/4441\">G4441</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1905/1905\">G1905</a>, <a href=\"#/G1906/1906\">G1906</a>, <a href=\"#/G2065/2065\">G2065</a>"}]}